[thinking] **Considering annotation generation**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about whether to allow native annotation proxy generation. It seems like existing metadata generated after previous Object/Reflection might not have an AnnotationHelper. I could add the resource manually to enable native features. However, if the agent runs, it might collect library dynamic access rather than running tests. I wonder if we can inspect the old build report to find insights. There's a lot to consider here!
